  <brief_title>Safety of TG100-115 for Heart Attack Treated With Angioplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1-2, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled, Prospective Study to Evaluate the Safety and Potential Efficacy of Single, Increasing Doses of TG100-115 in Subjects Undergoing Percutaneous Coronary Intervention for Acute Anterior ST Elevation Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
