      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>TargeGen</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      TG100-115 is able to reduce the size of heart attacks in pre-clinical models. The hypothesis
      of this study is that TG100-115 can be given safely to patients who suffer a heart attack and
      undergo angioplasty to restore blood flow. We will also evaluate whether TG100-115 reduces
      heart muscle damage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
